<h3><span id="Traductions_en_fran.C3.A7ais"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Traductions_en_français">Traductions en français</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rudyard_Kipling&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=13" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Traductions en français">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rudyard_Kipling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Modifier la section : Traductions en français">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
